Contributor Checkout → POST /storefront/transaction
   → GET /dispute-log/{id}
       → IF fraud alert → POST /fraud-alert-verify
   → PUT /audit-log/maadi
   → Dashboard → order + compliance status
   → IF failure → Recovery Path
       → Collect Logs → Validate Env → Retry
       → Incident → Quarantine firearm bundle until cleared
   → Legacy Broadcast → compliance proof snapshot (serial + hash)
